\c 23
\s Jehovha mufudzi wangu
\d Pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Jehovha ndiye mufudzi wangu; Hapana chandingashaiwa.
\v 2 Anondivatisa pasi pamafuro manyoro; Anondisesedza pamvura inozorodza.
\v 3 Anoponesa mweya wangu; Anondifambisa panzira dzokururama
\s nokuda kwezita rake.
\p
\v 4 Zvirokwazvo, kunyange ndikafamba mumupata womumvuri worufu, Handingatongotyi zvakaipa;
\s nokuti imi muneni;
\s Tsvimbo yenyu nomudonzvo
\s wenyu zvinondinyaradza.
\p
\v 5 Munondigadzirira chokudya pamberi pavadzivisi vangu;
\s Makazodza musoro wangu namafuta;
\p mukombe wangu unopfachuka.
\v 6 Zvirokwazvo unyoro nenyasha zvichanditevera mazuva ose
\s oupenyu hwangu;
\s Ini ndichagara mumba maJehovha mazuva namazuva.
